{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fac4c654cd","title":"上海市革命委员会批发“关于抄家问题审批权限的请示报告”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ebfcdd6a29","index":0,"year":1968,"month":1,"day":18,"articleId":"fac4c654cd","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"地方革委会","id":"0245b7c49b","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"革命委员会","id":"1d084c925f","type":"主题"},{"name":"公安与法律","id":"53b954d860","type":"主题"},{"name":"破四旧","id":"9ec766296f","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0929801515","type":"title","text":"上海市革命委员会批发“关于抄家问题审批权限的请示报告”","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d48601c41","type":"paragraph","text":"市革命委员会同意政法指挥部“关于抄家问题审批权限的请示报告”，请按照执行。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"55d4176834","type":"paragraph","text":"上海市革命委员会","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"01a59973e5","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六八年一月十八日","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9afa992b69","type":"paragraph","text":"关于抄家问题审批权限的请示报告","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b492bde32b","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥、文元同志并市革命委员会：","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a4f7fbd35","type":"paragraph","text":"随着当前上海无产阶级文化大革命的深入发展，革命群众要求抄家的情况日益增多，为了有力地支持广大革命群众的革命行动，巩固和加强无产阶级专政，根据中央和市革命委员会的有关指示精神，对一小撮走资派、叛徒、特务、未改造好的地富反坏右、资产阶级分子，掌握了一定罪证材料需要进行抄家进一步求得罪证的、在批准抄家权限方面，提出如下意见：","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9208235b55","type":"paragraph","text":"一、凡需对原副部（局）长和区、县级以上人员、市级民主党派代表人物进行抄家的，由所在单位革委会（筹备小组）或革命群众组织，请示市革委会有关组同意后，呈市革命委员会批准，由市公安局执行。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9420cd808","type":"paragraph","text":"二、凡需对原正副处长级人员进行抄家的，由所在单位革委会（筹备小组）或革命群众组织提出意见，经市革委会有关组审查后，由政法指挥部审批。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62ef578049","type":"paragraph","text":"三、凡需对原正副科长及其以下人员进行抄家的，由区、县革委会（筹备小组）审批，不属区、县范围的，由市公安部审批。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7efa21a7c9","type":"paragraph","text":"抄家是一项政策性很强的工作，应从严掌握。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c686d5d91","type":"paragraph","text":"批准抄家的对象，均由公安机关办理法律手续，协助群众组织执行。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fafcf50851","type":"paragraph","text":"今后中央对抄家问题如有新的指示，按中央指示执行。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"567a60e156","type":"paragraph","text":"上述意见，妥否，请批发。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69db40b0e8","type":"paragraph","text":"上海市革命委员会政法指挥部","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd87455731","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年十二月二十九日","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fac4c654cd","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}